### Welcome benjaminDev

This is a collection of my work and side projects. Unfortunately most is still private. I hope to do work that is open but as of now that is how it is.

My interests are in:
* Image Processing
* Digital Signal Processing
* Radar
* Anything Software related
* Visualizations
* Outdoor activities: Rock climbing, mountain biking, surfing.


Skill Set:
* C++, Python, C#, Matlab
* TDD (gtest), Git
